{"tid":1280033,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"想自盡嘅人 做就輸了","createTime":"2019-07-02T23:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T00:31:48.000Z","uid":91648,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f9a9ecb22aafa855c6a25b73b39c455f20775f","tid":1280033,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:54:50.000Z","msg":"這一代年青人難得有一腔熱血，應該成家立室，將正確觀念繁衍下去，而不是自己輕生希望死諫。<br />\n<br />\n你死左，政府都唔會可憐你，只會從大陸繼續殖入人口填補你嘅位置，這樣一進一出，香港本地抗爭又會少左，投票又少左。<br />\n<br />\n記住，留得青山在！"},{"pid":"ec79017c40d8c10d07974926742749fc1f840105","tid":1280033,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:56:59.000Z","msg":"養自己都無能力<br />\n<br />\n成家垃圾就有你份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3de8ccdd8ff652cfad73d1439a20c6857befc18","tid":1280033,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:58:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee98ec0e279437940053bcd7a1ecc06f8963170b","tid":1280033,"uid":100347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:24:30.000Z","msg":"有勇氣自殺<br />\n無勇氣令自己變得更強<br />\n無勇氣拉埋賣港賊一齊走<br />\n<br />\n孫中山不下十次先贏到<br />\n<br />\n人地絕望 做死士<br />\n呢啲人絕望就自殺<br />\n<br />\n要死由佢啦<br />\n少一件負能量來源 無咩所謂"},{"pid":"97e0061e45035d7f75af423d72835f812f20bb74","tid":1280033,"uid":18845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:31:48.000Z","msg":"留得青山在<br />\n<br />\n但問題係 人地想成坐山剷平你 <br />\n<br />\n可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}